{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-010__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-010", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·010.1", "text_original": "信彼南山，維禹甸之。畇畇原隰，曾孫田之。我疆我理，南東其畝。", "text_normalized": "信彼南山，維禹甸之。畇畇原隰，曾孫田之。我疆我理，南東其畝。", "notes": "信南山 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-010__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-010", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·010.2", "text_original": "上天同雲，雨雪雰雰。益之以霢霂，既優既渥。既霑既足，生我百穀。", "text_normalized": "上天同雲，雨雪雰雰。益之以霢霂，既優既渥。既霑既足，生我百穀。", "notes": "信南山 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-010__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-010", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·010.3", "text_original": "疆埸翼翼，黍稷彧彧。曾孫之穡，以為酒食。畀我尸賓，壽考萬年。", "text_normalized": "疆埸翼翼，黍稷彧彧。曾孫之穡，以為酒食。畀我尸賓，壽考萬年。", "notes": "信南山 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-010__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-010", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·010.4", "text_original": "中田有廬，疆埸有瓜。是剝是菹，獻之皇祖。曾孫壽考，受天之祜。", "text_normalized": "中田有廬，疆埸有瓜。是剝是菹，獻之皇祖。曾孫壽考，受天之祜。", "notes": "信南山 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-010__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-010", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·010.5", "text_original": "祭以清酒，從以騂牡，享于祖考。執其鸞刀，以啟其毛，取其血膋。", "text_normalized": "祭以清酒，從以騂牡，享于祖考。執其鸞刀，以啟其毛，取其血膋。", "notes": "信南山 Chinese stanza 5."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-010__006__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-010", "source_id": "xiaoya-gufeng-010__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·谷風之什·010.6", "text_original": "是烝是享，苾苾芬芬。祀事孔明，先祖是皇。報以介福，萬壽無疆。", "text_normalized": "是烝是享，苾苾芬芬。祀事孔明，先祖是皇。報以介福，萬壽無疆。", "notes": "信南山 Chinese stanza 6."}
